  "detailed_description": "<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >STORY:</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Third person action rpg game where player mission is to survive enough long in ruined forest land. Waves include goblins with melee weapons and also some waves include Big spiders with special attacks. Every wave has limited time to kill enemies. Game contains 8 waves and if player survive all waves, game is finished. Player can collect health potions, mana potions and also special hammer weapons. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >FEATURES:</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >8 waves</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >2 different enemies: basic goblins and big spider with special attacks</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >health potions</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Special hammers for limited time</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
